# 🔹 2. Comparison Operators

```python
# Comparison operators compare values

a = 13
b = 33

print(a > b)
print(a < b)
print(a == b)
print(a != b)
print(a >= b)
print(a <= b)
```

---

## ✅ Output

```python
False
True
False
True
False
True
```

---

## 📌 Comparison Operators

| Operator | Meaning          |
| -------- | ---------------- |
| >        | Greater than     |
| <        | Less than        |
| ==       | Equal            |
| !=       | Not equal        |
| >=       | Greater or equal |
| <=       | Less or equal    |

