# 🔹 6. Identity Operators

```python
# Identity operators compare memory locations

a = 10
b = 20
c = a

print(a is b)
print(a is c)

print(a is not b)
```

---

## ✅ Output

```python
False
True
True
```

---

## 📌 Identity Operators

| Operator | Meaning            |
| -------- | ------------------ |
| is       | Same memory object |
| is not   | Different objects  |

---

## 🎯 Interview Questions

* Difference between `==` and `is`
